{"tid":531754,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手閃光燈疑問求解","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T14:09:10.000Z","uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"532054bb5ce3f11a84199b002c1fc3e78cc3d44f","tid":531754,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"玩咗閃光燈冇耐 有樣嘢唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n點解一裝咗閃 快門就最多只可以去到1/250<br />\n冇得再快 有時環境太光（eg逆光）就算ISO 100都唔夠<br />\n要再收一收光圈 除咗咁其實有冇其他方法？<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇過幾編文 又話用閃係可以無視環境光 壓光我試過 但唔係次次得 應該同現場環境光有關<br />\n呢樣真係唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4aee4313dd9569bd80e0e9f05a9eae27cd943d","tid":531754,"uid":28001,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"你咩機咩閃？<br />\n一般超過1/250s flash sync<br />\n要support high speed sync 先得<br />\n要機同閃都support"},{"pid":"44e673942c981af94d128eaed0a97833a1b66d93","tid":531754,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"最高閃燈同步有限，因機而異<br />\n要突破限制就要用高速閃燈同步，但閃光power 會細左好多"},{"pid":"f09db0401bee1459084d2967cbad9801c3d4be50","tid":531754,"uid":28001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44e673942c981af94d128eaed0a97833a1b66d93","tid":531754,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"最高閃燈同步有限，因機而異<br />\n要突破限制就要用高速閃燈同步，但閃光power 會細左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:23:17.000Z","msg":"最多都係2-3 stop 左右<br />\n唔係用好tele 鏡應該問題唔大"},{"pid":"6645cbcc07a7eda672f82dcb51df139f34696c7e","tid":531754,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"支燈支援HSS就得"},{"pid":"1739dc94d17d7ede1e105465161ce10527db885a","tid":531754,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咩機咩閃？<br />\n一般超過1/250s flash sync<br />\n要support high speed sync 先得<br />\n要機同閃都support</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用Sony a7ii + 神牛350"},{"pid":"64b11591aecc4cd538042b33f0910d3bf8c4a09d","tid":531754,"uid":19900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"感謝咁多位解答 番去google吓hss先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50eae7278c069367f1d66872bd0ea48ca5b7a278","tid":531754,"uid":148075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1739dc94d17d7ede1e105465161ce10527db885a","tid":531754,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咩機咩閃？<br />\n一般超過1/250s flash sync<br />\n要support high speed sync 先得<br />\n要機同閃都support</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用Sony a7ii + 神牛350"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"tt350有高速同步<br />\n可以睇閃燈說明書點著高速同步"},{"pid":"065310de2ee8762f1a2cec5407369ece193e9c4a","tid":531754,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}